snippet.title: v6.8 Saha and Rebirth Trailer — Honkai Impact 3rd
snippet.description:
Honkai Impact 3rd v6.8 Saha and Rebirth coming soon! New S-rank Herrscher battlesuit Seele Vollerei Herrscher of Rebirth debuts!

Story Chapter XXXIX, Summer themed event Before the Endless Dream Ends, art collection event Hot Summer Gift! Book of Memories! and login rewards to be released! Stay tuned!

Voice Artists:

Seele Vollerei: Mai Nakahara
Shigure Kira: Ibuki Kido
PROMETHEUS: Kana Asumi
Schrodinger: Megumi Han
